ðŸ“„ Rooster Class Documentation

Class Name: Rooster
Language: Java

Description:

The Rooster class is an abstract class representing the combat units in the Cock Clashers game. Each rooster has attributes such as health points (HP), attack, defense, type, and skills. This class provides core mechanics for battle interactions, including taking damage, healing, attacking, and applying type-based damage multipliers.

It also handles sprite management for both front and back images, enabling visual representation during battles. Specific rooster types are implemented as subclasses with unique attributes and skills.

Key Features:

Stores and manages rooster stats (HP, attack, defense, type).

Manages skills and supports adding multiple skills per rooster.

Handles battle mechanics such as damage calculation, type effectiveness, and critical hits.

Provides sprite loading for visual representation in the game.

Supports fainting checks and full healing.


