Subclasses:

Subclass	Description

ManokNaPula	Fire-type rooster with fire-based skills like Flame Peck and Burning Crow.
ManokNaItim	Dark-type rooster with shadow-based attacks.
ManokNaBato	Rock-type rooster with stone and scratch skills.


Algorithm / Process Overview:

1. Initialization: Load sprites and initialize stats.


2. Battle:

Use attack() with a chosen skill.

Calculate damage: max(skillDamage - enemyDefense, MIN_DAMAGE).

Apply type multiplier from TypeEffectiveness.

Apply critical hit chance.

Reduce enemy HP.



3. Healing / Fainting:

healFull() restores HP.

isFainted() checks if HP â‰¤ 0.





---

Benefits:

Provides a modular and extendable framework for different rooster types.

Encapsulates battle logic and type-based damage mechanics.

Supports skill system with easy addition of new abilities.

Integrates seamlessly with GUI and game engine rendering.


